  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall, broad objective of this study is to pilot the BSD technique. The specific
      purpose of this particular study is to generate pilot data to validate several crucial steps
      of the BSD technique, in particular steps 1, 2, and 4. Radiation treatments will proceed per
      standard of care, and will not be modified in any way during this protocol. This study is a
      non-treatment protocol.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
